Book::Collate

Collates text files into a single large text file.
 - Provides a grade level report, as well as word usage counts.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Book::Collate

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker (report bugs here)
        https://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Book::Collate

    CPAN Ratings
        https://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Book::Collate

    Search CPAN
        https://metacpan.org/release/Book::Collate


